1972;;Sitting Target;;American;;Douglas Hickox;;Oliver Reed, Jill St. John;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sitting_Target;;Harry Lomart, a convicted murderer, and Birdy Williams are convicts planning a breakout. Before the two men can abscond to another country, Lomart gets word that his wife Pat has been having an affair with another man and has become pregnant.<br><br>The two men had made plans to lie low after their escape from jail, but Lomart decides to find and kill his wife and the man she has been seeing. A police inspector, Milton, is the man assigned to catch the two escaped convicts.